557
00:53:10,640 --> 00:53:17,120
You don't have the same kind of confusion or 
learning curve problem. And then if you start  

558
00:53:17,120 --> 00:53:22,720
out being too far leaned in, then you lean out too 
far. And I think a lot of that founder mode flip  

559
00:53:22,720 --> 00:53:29,240
