560
00:53:29,240 --> 00:53:35,600
I need to stop making excuses. And basically, 
I also don't want to apologize or negotiate all  

561
00:53:35,600 --> 00:53:41,960
the time for the kind of company that I want to 
be part of and run. So I had that too over time,  

562
00:53:41,960 --> 00:53:50,760
maybe more towards a chapter three, some of those 
elements of... And I don't know if there's a way  

